r7468 | eicker | 2009-05-08 15:06:17 +0200 (Fri, 08 May 2009) | 10 lines

Bugfix: Eliminate possible list-confusion in RDP during conn. close.
Bugfix: Really send new master in DD_MASTER_IS message.
